---
title: Bacon & Roast Broccoli Spaghetti with Parmesan Cheese
description: Roasted broccoli and crispy bacon may not be the first combo you think of when it comes to pasta, but you can trust us on this one!  Mix it all into a rich tomato-based sauce for a flavour explosion that’s even worthy of Nonna’s picky palate.
